---
description: Execution rules for long-running Cursor work in GroundSealWorkflowRuntime
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Start from README, PROJECT_BRIEF, roadmap, and tasks.
- Prefer docs -> contracts -> tests -> implementation.
- Every substantial work round should leave a visible durable artifact.
- Update roadmap or task sequencing before large changes in direction.
- Record failures and unexpected findings instead of silently routing around them.
